title: 10: How I got Arrested on my 18th Birthday
description: IT'S PARTY TIME F*CKERS! Come along for Sadies 18th birthday and experience it all. In this episode she takes you on a journey over to Florida  State University to celebrate her big eighteenth, aka a sh*t show. Getting put in the back of a cop car is just one of the funny things you get to hear all about. BUCKLE UP PEOPLE!
